django-mailer by James Tauber <http://jtauber.com/>
http://code.google.com/p/django-mailer/

A reusable Django app for queuing the sending of email



## Forked to add support for queueing X emails per day.
----------------------------------------------------

Google apps free version has a limit for sending 500 emails a day.
Forked to add throttling.

Now takes an optional DAILY_SENDING_LIMIT setting that limits emails sent per 24 hours.